# New ports collection makefile for:	vitetris
# Date created:				27 April 2008
# Whom:					<smultron@midnightbsd.org>
#
# $MidnightBSD: mports/games/vitetris/Makefile,v 1.5 2008/09/06 22:08:56 laffer1 Exp $
